                        <interp inst="t18361212-name-291" type="given" value="RICHARD GABRIEL"></interp>RICHARD GABRIEL GABB</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 14.) I took the two pri<lb></lb>soners—I found two other handkerchiefs on the boy.</p>
